# â­ Hands-On Exercises (Day 2)

## Exercise 1 â€” Scanner Commands
```bash
ping 8.8.8.8
traceroute google.com
ss -tulnp
```

## Exercise 2 â€” Inspect Traffic
Use Wireshark:
- visit a website
- filter: `tcp.handshake`

## Exercise 3 â€” Burp Repeater
1. Capture a request
2. Send to Repeater
3. Modify URL parameter
4. Observe changes

## Exercise 4 â€” Nmap
```bash
nmap -sV -sC -A -Pn TARGET_IP
```

